fields.tiffin_description: Indulge in a satisfying veg lunch box featuring a harmonious duo of dal and rice. This traditional Indian meal offers a wholesome blend of flavors and nutrients, with aromatic lentil curry complementing fluffy basmati rice. Experience the comforting essence of homemade goodness in every delightful bite.

Savor the flavors of our Paneer Tikka Biryani, a mouth-watering fusion of aromatic basmati rice and succulent paneer tikka. This delightful biryani is packed with fragrant spices and herbs, offering a tantalizing culinary experience.

Indulge in our flavorful Chicken Biryani, a classic Indian dish loved by many. Tender chicken pieces marinated in aromatic spices, layered with fragrant basmati rice, and slow-cooked to perfection. This biryani is sure to tantalize your taste buds.

Enjoy a delightful assortment of vegetarian dishes with our Veggie Delight Box. This box features a mix of flavorful vegetarian curries, rice, and bread, providing a satisfying and wholesome meal experience.
Indulge in a lavish feast with our Chicken Feast Combo. This combo includes a variety of chicken delicacies, along with rice, bread, and salad, providing a sumptuous dining experience.
Fuel your day with our Vegan Power Box, packed with nutritious vegan dishes. This box offers a variety of plant-based proteins, grains, and veggies, ensuring a balanced and satisfying meal.
Nourish your body with our Healthy Veggie Box, filled with a variety of nutritious vegetarian dishes. This box is perfect for those seeking a balanced and wholesome meal option.
Indulge in a luxurious seafood spread with our Seafood Extravaganza tiffin. Savor the rich flavors of various seafood delicacies, expertly prepared to tantalize your taste buds.
Experience a burst of flavors with our Vegan Delight Platter. This platter offers a delightful selection of plant-based dishes, perfect for vegans and those seeking a healthy dining option.

Indulge in the flavors of India with our Classic Indian Thali. This traditional platter offers a delightful assortment of savory dishes, including dal, rice, paneer tikka masala, and more, served with assorted bread and accompaniments.

Treat yourself to our Chicken Feast Box, brimming with delectable chicken dishes that are sure to satisfy your cravings. Enjoy a mix of classic chicken tikka, butter chicken, and chicken biryani, accompanied by flavorful sides.

Experience the ultimate Veggie Delight Box, packed with an array of delicious vegetarian dishes. Enjoy classics like paneer tikka masala, chana masala, and mixed vegetable curry, served with fragrant rice and assorted bread.
Dive into a seafood extravaganza with our delectable seafood tiffin. Indulge in succulent fish curry, aromatic shrimp biryani, and flavorful crab masala, served with fragrant rice and crispy papadum.

Savor the goodness of plant-based cuisine with our Vegan Delight Box. Enjoy a variety of flavorful vegan dishes, including tofu curry, mixed vegetable stir-fry, and lentil soup, served with fragrant brown rice and roti.
